---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Artikel teknis networking, opini karir IT, dan cerita dari balik meja instruktur. Ditulis oleh Ferry Pratama.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Blog</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title" style="font-size:clamp(40px,5.5vw,68px);">
      Tulisan tentang networking, karir, <em>dan hal-hal di antaranya.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Teknis kalau perlu. Santai kalau bisa. Selalu jujur.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="border-bottom:none;">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; margin-bottom:28px; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:16px;">
      <div class="filter-wrap" role="group" aria-label="Filter topik">
        <button class="filter-btn active" data-filter="all">Semua</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="teknis">Teknis</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="karir">Karir</button>
        <button class="filter-btn" data-filter="opini">Opini</button>
      </div>
      <div class="eyebrow">{{ collections.posts.length }} tulisan</div>
    </div>

    <div class="posts-grid" id="postsGrid">
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card" data-tag="{{ post.data.tag }}">
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <span class="post-tag tag-{{ post.data.tag }}">{{ post.data.tag | capitalize }}</span>
          {% if post.data.youtube_url %}<span class="post-tag-video">▶ Ada video</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="post-title">{{ post.data.title | safe }}</div>
        <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>{{ post.date | postDate }}</span>
          {% if post.data.readtime %}<span>{{ post.data.readtime }} mnt baca</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
